EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO FOOD AND DRUGS -- UNIFORM CONTROLLED SUBSTANCES ACT --
OFFENSES AND PENALTIES
***
1 This act would provide that possession of one ounce (1 oz.) to one kilogram (1 kg.) of a
2 mixture or substance containing at least ten percent (10%) of fentanyl or its analogs would be
3 punishable by up to fifty years imprisonment and possession of more than one kilogram (1 kg.) of
4 a mixture or substance containing at least ten percent (10%) of fentanyl or its analogs would be
5 punishable by up to life imprisonment.
6 This act would take effect upon passage.
